title: I got all the Gold+ rewards except Victorious Maokai .-.
body: They even unlocked Maokai for me because I didn't own him and forgot the skin. I have the Gold Icon, the Border, the Victorious Ward Skin, the Silver Icon from Ranked Team and the Silver Border from Ranked Team. It's just missing the Victorious Maokai Skin.

replies.body: Yeah, there's been a few players reporting this.  There are some loose ends, so not everyone has all of their rewards just yet.  They are coming, so don't worry!  Hang tight!

> [{quoted}](name=Porocles,realm=NA,application-id=osqw6G4M,discussion-id=O8qOZk6k,comment-id=0000,timestamp=2016-11-10T19:01:44.693+0000)
>
> You may see that some content is still missing or that one player may have received them sooner than another, but don't worry!  Per the [Season 6 FAQ](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/page/2016-ranked-season-ends-soon), we aim to have this wrapped up by the 21st.  Hope that helps offer some ease!
